{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b32800146b","title":"给续范亭的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b9dbe64477","index":0,"year":1945,"month":10,"day":18,"articleId":"b32800146b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji20","name":"毛泽东全集第20卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji20.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji20":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c7b53cc236","type":"paragraph","text":"给续范亭的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"b32800146b"},{"id":"559ea2c28c","type":"paragraph","text":"1945年10月18日）范亭兄：示器。大势所道，使当局不能不签订双十协定，但其实现却尚是大问题。私利所面，他们尚不愿承认解放区，并正向解放区进军，此间题之解决，麻烦尚多。看你写字，精神甚好，尚望研究休养办法，多活许多年，看见中国民主政治的实现。敬祝健康！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"b32800146b"},{"id":"648f7b2783","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"b32800146b"},{"id":"cd9da065c3","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十八日百合果敬收，至谢！江青致侯[1]续范亭（1893-1947），山西省等县（今原平市）西社村人，著名爱国将领。早年参加孙中山领导的同题会。后在国民党任职，曾经隐退一段时间，后与共产党人合作创建山西新军。1947年榜蓝后被道认为中国共产党","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"b32800146b"}],"page":{"id":"c6a63c156b","publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"b32800146b","start":452,"end":452}}}},"__N_SSG":true}